---------------------------
 DDF Library
-----------------------------

The Distributed DataFrame Library (DDF Library) provides distributed algorithms and operations ready to use as a
library implemented over PyCOMPSs programming model.

Release number: 0.5
Release date: X-2020
-------------------------------

Improvements:

 - Improvements in operations like partitioning methods and merge schema by using COLLECTION COMPSs feature.
 - The data output of a COMPSs's task is a parquet file to speedup the des/serialization process.